---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import matcha from "../assets/images/matcha/matchaPowder.png";
import makeMatcha from "../assets/images/recipes/makeMatcha.svg";

import matchaField from "../assets/images/matcha/matcha-field.jpg";
import matchaTable from "../assets/images/matcha/matcha-table.png";

import HeadlineSection from "../components/sections/HeadlineSection.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import FAQSection from "../components/sections/FAQSection.astro";
import InputField from "../components/atoms/InputField.astro";
import Button from "../components/atoms/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout titleTag="So what is matcha?" pagename="about-matcha" metaDescription="Piohní specialize in authentic Japanese matcha because it’s Calming, Mood Enhancing, Energy Stabilizing and Rich in Antioxidants">
  <main>
    <section class="what-is-matcha">
      <div class="textBox">
        <HeadlineSection showButton="false" headline="So what is matcha?" subheadline="Matcha — 抹茶 — is essentially finely milled green tea powder known to be more nutrient than both tea and coffee. But to us, matcha is much more than that." />
        <div class="benefits">
          <div class="benefit">
            <h2 class="Typo-headline-xstrasmall-classic">Calming</h2>
            <p class="Typo-body-small">We specialize in authentic Japanese matcha because it's not just a coffee alternative — it's a moment of peace. With matcha, you take a sip, exhale, and feel "aaahhh."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h2 class="Typo-headline-xstrasmall-classic">Mood Enhancing</h2>
            <p class="Typo-body-small">Matcha is a mood lifting powerhouse. Loaded with L-theanine , it boosts serotonin for daily happiness and relaxation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h2 class="Typo-headline-xstrasmall-classic">Energy Stabilizing</h2>
            <p class="Typo-body-small">With its blend of caffeine and L-theanine, matcha offers lasting energy, keeping you focused longer — akin to Japanese monks during meditation sessions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h2 class="Typo-headline-xstrasmall-classic">Rich in Antioxidants</h2>
            <p class="Typo-body-small">Matcha is rich in antioxidants, with over 10 times the amount found in a standard cup of green tea. These antioxidants combat harmful molecules & reduce oxidative stress.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="matchaImage"><Image src={matcha} alt="matcha powder" class="image" /></div>
    </section>
    <FAQSection />
    <section class="cta_section">
      <div class="questionForm">
        <p class="Typo-headline-small-elegant">Do you still have questions?</p>
        <form action="">
          <InputField placeholder="E-mail" type="email" autocomplete="email" inputId="" />
          <textarea class="Typo-form-placeholder" name="question" form="ContactForm" placeholder="Write your question here..." required></textarea>

          <input type="submit" value="Send question" class="button Typo-button_label" id="formButton" />
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="spacerLine"></div>
      <div class="recipeLink">
        <p class="Typo-headline-small-elegant">Learn how to prepare matcha</p>
        <Image src={makeMatcha} alt="matcha illustration" class="image" />
        <div class="buttonContainer">
          <Button style="tertiary" label="Matcha Recipes" href="/recipes" size="fillContainer" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="history_section">
      <div class="history_container">
        <div class="text_container">
          <h2 class="Typo-headline-medium-uppercase story-headline">The History of Matcha</h2>
          <p class="Typo-body-regular">
            Matcha's story begins in ancient China, prized for its medicinal properties. But it truly flourished in Japan, thanks to Zen Buddhist monks who brought it over in the 12th century. Japanese monk Eisai played a key role, bringing tea seeds
            and the method of making powdered green tea back from China in 1191. He planted these seeds in Kyoto and promoted matcha for its health benefits, including improved focus and well-being.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="StoryImage_container"><Image src={matchaField} alt="matcha leaves" class="image" /></div>
        <div class="text_container">
          <p class="Typo-body-bold">How was matcha discovered?</p>
          <p class="Typo-body-regular">
            Legend has it that Monk Eisai, a Japanese Buddhist monk, was the one who introduced matcha to Japan in the 12th century. In 1191 he brought back tea seeds and the method of making powdered green tea from China. He planted these seeds in
            Kyoto and promoted matcha for its health benefits, including improved focus and well-being.<br /> Eisai's 1211 book, "Kissa Yojoki" ("The Book of Tea and Health"), highlighted matcha's healing properties and preparation methods, significantly
            influencing Japanese tea culture.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text_container">
          <p class="Typo-body-bold">Matcha today</p>
          <p class="Typo-body-regular">
            Today, matcha is a global sensation, celebrated for its unique flavour and calming effects. Like fine wine, it comes in various qualities. At Piohní, we've scoured the globe for the best ceremonial grade matcha. This once-exclusive drink
            is now a delightful, comforting treat for everyone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="HistoryImage_container"><Image src={matchaTable} alt="matcha leaves" class="image" /></div>
    </section>

    <style>
      /* what is matcha section */
      .what-is-matcha {
        display: flex;
        padding: 0 20px;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .textBox {
        display: flex;

        padding: 0px 20px;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 60px;
      }
      .benefits {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;

        gap: 40px 20px;
      }
      .benefit {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        flex: 1 0 0;
        min-width: 190px;
      }
      .benefit h2 {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .benefit p {
        max-width: 260px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      /* form */

      .spacerLine {
        height: 1px;
        width: 100%;
        background: var(--Color-Stroke-Secondary, #3d2d21);
      }
      .cta_section {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }
      .recipeLink .image {
        height: 168px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
      .questionForm,
      .recipeLink {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px;
        padding: 40px 0px;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
      }
      form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 345px;
      }
      textarea {
        border: 1px solid var(--Color-Stroke-Primary);
        color: var(--Color-Text-Body);
        padding: 10px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 108px;
      }
      textarea:focus {
        outline-color: var(--Color-Stroke-Blue);
      }
      #formButton {
        background-color: var(--Color-Fill-Button-Tertiary);
        border: none;
        box-shadow: 0px 1px 4px 0px var(--Color-Effect-Dropshadow-Button-Default);
        color: var(--Color-Text-White);
      }
      .button,
      .buttonContainer {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 345px;
      }

      /* history of matcha section */

      .history_section {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0px 40px;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 40px;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .history_container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 40px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .story-headline {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }
      .image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }
      p {
        max-width: 600px;
      }

      .StoryImage_container,
      .HistoryImage_container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        aspect-ratio: 480 / 251;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      @media (min-width: 500px) {
        .benefits {
          gap: 40px;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
      }
      @media (min-width: 700px) {
        .what-is-matcha {
          padding: 60px 20px 0;
        }
        .textBox {
          padding: 0 40px;
        }
        .cta_section {
          flex-direction: row;
          gap: 80px;
        }
        .spacerLine {
          width: 1px;
          height: 330px;
        }
        .button,
        .buttonContainer {
          max-width: 185px;
        }
        .history_section {
          padding: 0px 80px;
        }
      }
      @media (min-width: 980px) {
        .benefits {
          display: flex;
          gap: 20px;
          align-items: flex-start;
          align-self: stretch;
        }
        .history_section {
          flex-direction: row;
        }
        .StoryImage_container {
          display: none;
        }
        .HistoryImage_container {
          height: 100%;
          min-height: 612px;
          max-height: 828px;
        }
        .HistoryImage_container .image {
          object-position: center;
        }
      }
      @media (min-width: 1100px) {
        .what-is-matcha {
          padding: 100px 20px 0;
        }
        .textBox {
          padding: 0 80px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
